      <hedline>
        <hl1>CUNY Overhaul Assailed</hl1>
      </hedline>
    </body.head>
    <body.content>
      <block class="lead_paragraph">
        <p>A plan to overhaul academic programs throughout the City University of New York was denounced yesterday by dozens of faculty members, students, artists and intellectuals as an effort to destroy the university's attempts to provide a broad-based education for poor students. The criticism was made at a public hearing of the university's board at the Hunter College School of Social Work.</p>
      </block>
